headline: How Will Biden Lead? Look to His Campaign
text: Like President Bill Clinton, Joseph R. Biden Jr. is an empathetic extrovert with a sprawling network of friends. Like President George W. Bush, he maintains strict personal discipline (for Mr. Biden, that meant Peloton rides and protein shakes this year, to offset an ice cream habit).
snippet: He is returning to a Washington he knows well. And the path he took to get back offers a road map for how he’ll govern.
